Home // About Us


Comprehensive Financial Solutions Built For You


Driven by the notion of what is best for you, we build custom solutions that integrate the financial needs of high net worth individuals, their families and corporate clients. As your advocate, we take the time to deeply understand your goals and values and then develop strategies to help protect and preserve your wealth.
Backed by a team of highly trained professionals, our advisors have access to a broad range of financial solutions to assist you:

Financial Planning
Asset Management
Insurance & Risk Management
Employee Benefits
Executive Benefits

By building comprehensive plans where all the elements are working in unison, we can help you achieve what matters most — a strong financial future for you and your family.





Investment Advisor calls Lenox's business model the best in industry, “the epitome of wealth management done right.”

