How do I update this listing?




                                             Lenox Wealth Advisors is based out of New York. Lenox Wealth Advisors is a large advisory firm with  More than 100 clients and discretionary assets under management (AUM) of $856,675,041 (Form ADV from 2017-03-30).  Their last reported 13F filing for Q2 2017 included $305,468,000 in managed 13F securities
    and a top 10 holdings concentration of 95.89%. Lenox Wealth Advisors's largest holding is SPDR S&P 500 ETF Index Depositary Receipts with shares held of 284,869.  Lenox Wealth Advisors has met the qualifications for inclusion in our WhaleScore system.    WhaleWisdom has at least 20 13F filings in our database for Lenox Wealth Advisors. 
                                           






